  "markup": "\u003Cp\u003EAs a company, we\u2019ve adopted a dress code that leans more casual. We like to foster comfort and confidence. The only three things we ask are:\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\u0026nbsp;\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp style=\u0022padding-left: 30px;\u0022\u003E1. Make sure that your clothing and appearance are clean and professional.\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp style=\u0022padding-left: 30px;\u0022\u003E2. If a work event requires a more formal dress code, please dress it up.\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp style=\u0022padding-left: 30px;\u0022\u003E3. If you are unsure about what is appropriate for a situation, just ask. You should reach out to your manager or the HR Team.\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\u0026nbsp;\u003C/p\u003E"
}]]></Value>
